<p>Top line (0, 00, 1, 2, 3) has a different expected value because of <a h=
ref=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Approximation" title=3D"Approximation"=
>approximation</a> of the correct <link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style=
" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1154941027"><span class=3D"frac">6<span c=
lass=3D"sr-only">+</span><span class=3D"num">1</span>=E2=81=84<span class=
=3D"den">5</span></span>-to-1 payout obtained by the formula to 6-to-1.
</p><p>If <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/En_prison" title=3D"E=
n prison">en prison</a></i> rules are used, the house edge on the 1:1 bets =
is reduced to 1.35%-1.38% on a single-zero wheel,<sup id=3D"cite_ref-10" cl=
ass=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roulette#cite_no=
te-10"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>10<span class=3D"cite-bracket">=
]</span></a></sup> and to 2.63% on a double-zero wheel.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-=
11" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roulette#c=
ite_note-11"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>11<span class=3D"cite-bra=
cket">]</span></a></sup>
</p>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"House_edge">House edge</h2>=
<span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</sp=
an><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DRoulette&amp;act=
ion=3Dedit&amp;section=3D10" title=3D"Edit section: House edge"><span>edit<=
/span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>The <i>house average</i> or <i>house edge</i> or <i>house advantage</i> =
(also called the <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Expected_value=
" title=3D"Expected value">expected value</a></i>) is the amount the player=
 loses relative to any bet made, on average. If a player bets on a single n=
umber in the American game there is a probability of <link rel=3D"mw-dedupl=
icated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1154941027"><span clas=
s=3D"frac"><span class=3D"num">1</span>=E2=81=84<span class=3D"den">38</spa=
n></span> that the player wins 35 times the bet, and a <link rel=3D"mw-dedu=
plicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1154941027"><span cl=
ass=3D"frac"><span class=3D"num">37</span>=E2=81=84<span class=3D"den">38</=
span></span> chance that the player loses their bet. The expected value is:
</p>
<dl><dd>=E2=88=921 =C3=97 <link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=
=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1154941027"><span class=3D"frac"><span class=3D=
"num">37</span>=E2=81=84<span class=3D"den">38</span></span> + 35 =C3=97 <l=
ink rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r11=
54941027"><span class=3D"frac"><span class=3D"num">1</span>=E2=81=84<span c=
lass=3D"den">38</span></span> =3D =E2=88=920.0526 (5.26% house edge)</dd></=
dl>
<p>For European roulette, a single number wins <link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated=
-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1154941027"><span class=3D"f=
rac"><span class=3D"num">1</span>=E2=81=84<span class=3D"den">37</span></sp=
an> and loses <link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:Te=
mplateStyles:r1154941027"><span class=3D"frac"><span class=3D"num">36</span=
>=E2=81=84<span class=3D"den">37</span></span>:
</p>
<dl><dd>=E2=88=921 =C3=97 <link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=
=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1154941027"><span class=3D"frac"><span class=3D=
"num">36</span>=E2=81=84<span class=3D"den">37</span></span> + 35 =C3=97 <l=
ink rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r11=
54941027"><span class=3D"frac"><span class=3D"num">1</span>=E2=81=84<span c=
lass=3D"den">37</span></span> =3D =E2=88=920.0270 (2.70% house edge)</dd></=
dl>
<p>For triple-zero wheels, a single number wins <link rel=3D"mw-deduplicate=
d-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1154941027"><span class=3D"=
frac"><span class=3D"num">1</span>=E2=81=84<span class=3D"den">39</span></s=
pan> and loses <link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:T=
emplateStyles:r1154941027"><span class=3D"frac"><span class=3D"num">38</spa=
n>=E2=81=84<span class=3D"den">39</span></span>:
</p>
<dl><dd>=E2=88=921 =C3=97 <link rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=
=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1154941027"><span class=3D"frac"><span class=3D=
"num">38</span>=E2=81=84<span class=3D"den">39</span></span> + 35 =C3=97 <l=
ink rel=3D"mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href=3D"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r11=
54941027"><span class=3D"frac"><span class=3D"num">1</span>=E2=81=84<span c=
lass=3D"den">39</span></span> =3D =E2=88=920.0769 (7.69% house edge)</dd></=
dl>
<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id=3D"Mathematical_model">Mathema=
tical model</h2><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsectio=
n-bracket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3D=
Roulette&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D11" title=3D"Edit section: Mathema=
tical model"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]<=
/span></span></div>
