m Russia with Love</i></a> in Italy, attended the casino in <a href=3D"http=
s://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saint-Vincent,_Aosta_Valley" title=3D"Saint-Vince=
nt, Aosta Valley">Saint-Vincent</a> and won three consecutive times on the =
number 17, his winnings <i>riding</i> on the second and third spins.<sup id=
=3D"cite_ref-22" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wi=
ki/Roulette#cite_note-22"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>22<span clas=
s=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>In the early 1990s, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?tit=
le=3DGonzalo_Garc%C3%ADa-Pelayo&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;redlink=3D1" class=3D=
"new" title=3D"Gonzalo Garc=C3=ADa-Pelayo (page does not exist)">Gonzalo Ga=
