the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Casino_de_Madrid" title=3D"Cas=
ino de Madrid">Casino de Madrid</a> in <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/=
wiki/Madrid" title=3D"Madrid">Madrid</a>, Spain, winning 600,000 euros in a=
 single day, and two million euros in total. Legal action against him by th=
e casino was unsuccessful, it being ruled that the casino should fix its wh=
eel.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-23" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikip=
