</span></a></sup></li>
<li>In 2004, <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ashley_Revell" title=
=3D"Ashley Revell">Ashley Revell</a> of London sold all of his possessions,=
 clothing included, and placed his entire net worth of US$135,300 on red at=
 the <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Plaza_Hotel_%26_Casino" title=
=3D"Plaza Hotel &amp; Casino">Plaza Hotel</a> in Las Vegas. The ball landed=
 on "Red 7" and Revell walked away with $270,600.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-BBC_25=
-0" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roulette#c=
